OL,3,CLoose Women launch domestic abuse
OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,FBy Abeer Musawaei and Katie Andrews
OL,8,FAn ITV Loose Women campaign aimed at
OL,9,Fhighlighting help available for people
OL,10,Fliving with domestic-abuse - as well
OL,11,Fas how to spot signs of an abusive
OL,12,Frelationship - has been launched in
OL,13,FBelfast.
OL,15,FThe campaign was launched in the
OL,16,Fcity's Castlecourt shopping centre.
