OL,3,CLoose Women launch domestic abuse
OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,FPSNI figures show there were over
OL,7,F32,000 domestic abuse incidents in the
OL,8,Fyear up to June 2025. On average a
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse incident was reported
OL,10,Fevery 16 minutes.
OL,12,FWomen's Aid, Justice Minister Naomi
OL,13,FLong, and the PSNI welcomed Loose
OL,14,FWomen's "Facing it Together" campaign
OL,15,Fwhich sees the rollout on posters
OL,16,Faround the UK highlighting the
OL,17,Fdevastating effects of domestic abuse.
