OL,3,CLoose Women launch domestic abuse
OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,F"A few years ago nobody really knew
OL,7,Fwords such as 'coercive control,' but
OL,8,Fcoercive control is something that can
OL,9,Fcreep up and do so much damage.
OL,11,F"People always talked about the actual
OL,12,Fphysical violence, but coercive
OL,13,Fcontrol is keeping women quiet, and
OL,14,Ftheir pain secret because they think
OL,15,Fit's so embarrassing and it's
OL,16,Fsomething that they were doing was
OL,17,Fwrong.
OL,19,F"We want to break open that
OL,20,Fconversation with people," Nadia said.
