OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,FITV broadcast part of Loose Women live
OL,7,Ffrom the campaign launch in
OL,8,FCastlecourt.
OL,10,FSarah Mason, CEO at Women's Aid
OL,11,FFederation added: "It's a brave step
OL,12,Fbut a powerful one to get us on the
OL,13,Froad of shifting society and actioning
OL,14,Fchange.
OL,16,F"Everyone has seen really famous faces
OL,17,Fbehind it with really strong messages."
