OL,3,CLoose Women launch domestic abuse
OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,FSarah added: "There's a bit of
OL,7,Fpositive shifts and legislation we
OL,8,Fwork very closely with from place to
OL,9,Fplace. We wanted the judicial system
OL,10,Fto hold perpetrators to account and
OL,11,Fthat's about courts.
OL,13,F"We want appropriate sentencing but
OL,14,Fmost important making sure that the
OL,15,Fvictim does, because it isn't always
OL,16,Fthey want to go to court, it's about
OL,17,Fthem leaving support both for them and
OL,18,Ftheir children.
OL,20,FThe PSNI said domestic abuse was a
OL,21,Fpriority for its officers.
