OL,3,CLoose Women launch domestic abuse
OL,4,Cawareness campaign in Belfast
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Zoe
OL,7,FMcKee, Head of Public Protection
OL,8,FBranch at PSNI commented: "Domestic
OL,9,Fabuse is a life changing crime that
OL,10,Faffects all our communities.
OL,12,F"We are making, on average, 84 arrests
OL,13,Feach month for domestic related
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,16,F"It's also about how we stand with
OL,17,Fthem, how we align our work with them,
OL,18,Fbut also how we prosecute and
OL,19,Fprosecute offenders."
